&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specific responsibilities may include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish fire protection requirements that inform plant design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;428&quot;&gt;Develop Fire Hazard Analyses, Fire Protection Program, First Safe Shutdown Analyses, and other licensing and design documentation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define equipment architecture, specifications, operational modes, and performance criteria&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design of fire protection equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform commissioning and testing of fire protection systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage projects with third party fire protection consultants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1231&quot;&gt;Document work using modern tools and techniques, and compose well-written, thoughtful technical reports&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2299&quot;&gt;Engineering education, potentially Fire Protection, Nuclear, Chemical, or Mechanical&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2394&quot;&gt;Experience performing design of fire protection systems&amp;nbsp;in the nuclear, petroleum, petrochemical, or pharmaceutical industries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2597&quot;&gt;Broad familiarity with engineering principles, and having strong systems engineering and operations intuition&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competencies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Fire Protection Engineer that is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgable in nuclear facility fire protection design and operations under an NRC or DOE license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;950&quot;&gt;Experienced with NFPA 804 or NFPA 850&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;950&quot;&gt;Experience with IBC or IFC standards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1020&quot;&gt;Passionate about making advanced fission a reality&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1074&quot;&gt;Willing and able to learn quickly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1111&quot;&gt;Willing to think differently and do things in new ways&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1170&quot;&gt;Comfortable in a fast-paced, highly iterative startup environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1239&quot;&gt;Excited to think creatively, critically, and reflectively about the problems they are solving while not leaning only on what has been done before&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1389&quot;&gt;Willing to propose novel and creative solutions to technical problems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1462&quot;&gt;An excellent writer who can write in a modern active voice, so make your cover letter compelling and write it well!&lt;/p&gt;
