&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competencies:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;756&quot;&gt;We are looking for exceptional individuals that are:&lt;/p&gt;
