&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in design, prototyping and manufacturing operations, preferably in the nuclear, energy, or high-regulated industry, with at least 3 years in a leadership or excellence-focused role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to lead teams, coach cross-functional groups, and drive cultural change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in CAD design tools&lt;/li&gt;
