&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;513&quot; data-local-id=&quot;dd97eaa8d064&quot;&gt;The Manager, Supply Chain Systems Transformation is responsible for designing, implementing, and continuously improving the systems, processes, analytics, and operational infrastructure that enable Oklo’s supply chain organization to scale from development activities to fleet deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
