&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1027&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5157bbc83823&quot;&gt;Troubleshoot network connectivity issues across user endpoints, conference rooms, labs, and office environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1027&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5157bbc83823&quot;&gt;Assist with network configuration tasks such as VLANs, DNS, DHCP, and IP addressing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1027&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5157bbc83823&quot;&gt;Support VPN and secure remote access solutions in coordination with the IT/Cyber team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
