&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1473&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f8eb9fdab588&quot;&gt;Provide hands-on support for user endpoints running macOS, Ubuntu/Linux, and Windows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1473&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f8eb9fdab588&quot;&gt;Assist with provisioning, setup, and maintenance of endpoint devices and peripherals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1473&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f8eb9fdab588&quot;&gt;Support basic server and virtualization environments (e.g., VMware) as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1473&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f8eb9fdab588&quot;&gt;Manage user access and device connectivity using tools such as JumpCloud, Jamf, Intune, or equivalent platforms&lt;/li&gt;
