&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;&quot;&gt;Eager to work on a dynamic team, receive constructive feedback, and grow with us&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;&quot;&gt;Willing to think differently and do things in new ways&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;&quot;&gt;Comfortable in a fast-paced, highly iterative startup environment&lt;/li&gt;
